[24.132194, "o", "\r\n2.3. Executing HIERARCHY pass (managing design hierarchy).\r\n\r\n2.3.1. Analyzing design hierarchy..\r\nTop module:  \\AuroraUartTop\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraSerialiser\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraGenUart\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraUartTx\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraUartRx\r\n\r\n2.3.2. Analyzing design hierarchy..\r\nTop module:  \\AuroraUartTop\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraSerialiser\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraGenUart\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraUartTx\r\nUsed module:     \\AuroraUartRx\r\nRemoved 0 unused modules.\r\n\r\n2.4. Executing PROC pass (convert processes to netlists).\r\n\r\n2.4.1. Executing PROC_CLEAN pass (remove empty switches from decision trees).\r\nCleaned up 0 empty switches.\r\n\r\n2.4.2. Executing PROC_RMDEAD pass (remove dead branches from decision trees).\r\nMarked 6 switch rules as full_case in process $proc$/workspace/.artifacts/aurora_uart/hw.sv:411$241 in module AuroraUartTx.\r\nMarked 13 switch rules as full_case in process $proc$/workspace/.artifacts/aurora_uart/hw.sv:327$218 in module AuroraSerialiser.\r\nMarked 24 switch rules as full_case in process $proc$/workspace/.artifacts/aurora_uart/hw.sv:133$17 in module AuroraGenUart.\r\nMarked 7 switch rules as full_case in process $proc$/workspace/.artifacts/aurora_uart/hw.sv:41$1 in module AuroraUartRx.\r\nRemoved a total of 0 dead cases.\r\n\r\n2.4.3. Executing PROC_PRUNE pass (remove redundant assignments in processes).\r\nRemoved 2 redundant assignments.\r\nPromoted 0 assignments to connections.\r\n\r\n2.4.4. Executing PROC_INIT pass (extract init attributes).\r\n\r\n2.4.5. Executing PROC_ARST pass (detect async resets in processes).\r\n\r\n2.4.6. Executing PROC_ROM pass (convert switches to ROMs).\r\nConverted 0 switches.\r\n<suppressed ~59 debug messages>\r\n\r\n2.4.7. Executing PROC_MUX pass (convert decision trees to multiplexers).\r\nCreating decoders for process `\\AuroraUartTx.$proc$/workspace/.artifacts/aurora_uart/hw.sv:411$241'.\r\n     1/6: $0\\tx_r