[34.173622, "o", "\r\nFlash complete.\r\nIMPORTANT: The GW2AR-18C does not always reload from flash after a JTAG reset.\r\nIf the FPGA does not respond: unplug and replug the USB cable to power-cycle it.\r\n"]
[34.173777, "o", "The chip loads the bitstream from external flash automatically on power-on.\r\n"]
